36:56.960 --> 36:58.130
- No one's gonna get hurt

36:58.130 --> 37:00.510
unless we fail in stopping the alien.

37:00.510 --> 37:01.620
We have reason to believe

37:01.620 --> 37:03.410
the visitor is attempting to construct

37:03.410 --> 37:05.420
weapons of mass destruction.

37:05.420 --> 37:08.740
