37:08.740 --> 37:11.110
- I don't care about your weapons, Spears.

37:11.110 --> 37:12.760
It's personal now.

37:12.760 --> 37:15.410
That alien will be coming with me tonight,

37:15.410 --> 37:17.201
that I can guarantee.

37:17.201 --> 37:20.330
- Just make sure he comes in
alive and in one piece, Ricky,

37:20.330 --> 37:22.490
or there's gonna be
some harsh consequences,

37:22.490 --> 37:23.690
if you know what I mean.

37:26.460 --> 37:29.349
- Alive or dead, don't
make no difference to me.

38:04.125 --> 38:05.993
- They got guns.

38:05.993 --> 38:07.500
They got peek-a-boos, too.

38:08.440 --> 38:09.740
- Yes Randy.

38:09.740 --> 38:11.650
It seems there's no way in.

38:11.650 --> 38:14.720
Just remember, that things
look darkest just before

38:14.720 --> 38:16.143
it all goes pitch black.

38:17.630 --> 38:19.973
- You sure know English good now.

38:21.290 --> 38:23.450
- I've been experimenting, Randy.

38:23.450 --> 38:25.610
It seems I can do things on this planet

38:25.610 --> 38:27.984
that were impossible on my planet,

38:27.984 --> 38:31.410
like sending out the energy surges.

38:31.410 --> 38:34.565
- Yeah, and the bubble.

38:34.565 --> 38:36.960
- Yes, like the force field bubble.

38:36.960 --> 38:39.690
Take my hand, Randy, and close your eyes.

38:39.690 --> 38:40.873
I'll get us inside.

38:43.850 --> 38:45.560
Randy, look in my eyes.

38:48.159 --> 38:50.637
We must focus on love for each other.

38:50.637 --> 38:53.790
Love is the source of all my power.

38:53.790 --> 38:55.290
I love you, Randy.

38:56.532 --> 38:59.032
- I love you, too, Space Bear.

39:16.295 --> 39:18.810
- Sir, Yogi is in the house.

39:18.810 --> 39:21.096
Repeat, Yogi's in the house.

39:44.990 --> 39:46.260
- Wait out here, Randy.

39:46.260 --> 39:48.880
The radiation inside will kill you.

39:48.880 --> 39:49.993
- Okay, Bearian.

39:50.991 --> 39:52.515
Be careful.

40:00.117 --> 40:04.700
- Put this in your backpack,
and let's get out of here.

40:34.057 --> 40:35.755
- You okay, Bearian?

40:40.123 --> 40:41.710
- Come on out, boy.

40:41.710 --> 40:43.810
Hand over the alien, and no one gets hurt.

40:44.887 --> 40:48.452
- Over my dead body, dirtbag.

41:20.640 --> 41:23.227
- You don't know who you're
messing with, numbnuts.

41:27.480 --> 41:28.313
Gotcha!

42:03.970 --> 42:05.770
- All right, show's over.

42:05.770 --> 42:07.123
The alien comes with us.

42:10.629 --> 42:11.462
- Granny!

42:20.574 --> 42:22.677
- These men are bad, Randy.

42:22.677 --> 42:25.313
Don't let me stand in the way.

42:25.313 --> 42:27.813
Save yourself and your friend.

42:28.925 --> 42:29.925
- No Granny!

42:39.348 --> 42:40.681
- Zowie!

42:44.313 --> 42:46.896
No!

42:56.709 --> 43:00.126
No!

43:16.570 --> 43:18.250
- Cease fire, cease fire!

43:18.250 --> 43:20.310
Stop wasting bullets, you morons.

43:20.310 --> 43:21.163
They're gone.

43:23.920 --> 43:26.550
Get this pansy to a doctor, will ya.

43:26.550 --> 43:28.890
And get somebody up here with a Sham-Wow.

43:28.890 --> 43:30.869
This place is a mess.

44:00.326 --> 44:03.187
- Not Granny, not Granny.

44:03.187 --> 44:04.104
Not Granny!

44:05.613 --> 44:08.770
- It's going to be okay, Randy.

44:08.770 --> 44:09.790
Don't worry.

44:09.790 --> 44:12.703
The Love Bomb is our only
hope to set things right.

44:39.270 --> 44:41.100
- Gitsburg will have to be disposed of

44:41.100 --> 44:43.460
once we have the alien in custody.

44:43.460 --> 44:44.950
He knows too much.

44:44.950 --> 44:47.180
We'll have to make it
look like an accident.

44:47.180 --> 44:48.410
In the meantime,

44:48.410 --> 44:50.993
I want everyone working
around the clock on this.

44:51.870 --> 44:54.340
- We have several reports of break-ins

44:54.340 --> 44:56.090
and thefts from junkyards,

44:56.090 --> 45:00.029
electronic stores, hardware
stores, you name it, sir.

45:00.029 --> 45:02.290
- I'm aware of that, Agent Smiley.

45:02.290 --> 45:03.870
If I didn't know any better,

45:03.870 --> 45:06.397
I'd say this alien is
trying to build a nuke.

45:06.397 --> 45:08.137
Time is of the essence.

45:08.137 --> 45:10.270
Somebody get Ricky on the horn,

45:10.270 --> 45:12.630
and tell him that if he
doesn't find that space bear

45:12.630 --> 45:14.070
by the end of the week,

45:14.070 --> 45:17.240
I'm gonna bring a hammer
straight down on his juevos.

45:17.240 --> 45:18.920
Now let's get to work.

45:36.840 --> 45:39.630
- I have everything I need
now to build a Love Bomb,

45:39.630 --> 45:41.853
but it will take time to assemble.

45:43.190 --> 45:45.330
We need to find a desolate place

45:45.330 --> 45:48.385
with no people to set off the Love Bomb.

45:48.385 --> 45:50.833
The explosion will be massive.

45:50.833 --> 45:53.630
Do you know of a place like this?

45:53.630 --> 45:56.420
- My daddy is from a place called Wyoming.

45:56.420 --> 45:59.580
Granny says there's nothing
there but sheep shagging,

45:59.580 --> 46:01.700
whatever that is.

46:01.700 --> 46:03.670
- Wyoming, yes.

46:03.670 --> 46:05.610
I have read of this land,

46:05.610 --> 46:09.010
the land of sheep shaggers, as you say.

46:09.010 --> 46:13.110
We must leave for Wyoming once
the Love Bomb is complete.

46:13.110 --> 46:14.440
- Okay, Bearian.

46:14.440 --> 46:15.747
I'll go with you.

46:15.747 --> 46:18.633
- I'm so sorry about Granny, Randy.

46:19.659 --> 46:21.220
- It's okay.

46:21.220 --> 46:22.243
It's not your fault.

46:23.358 --> 46:26.380
- We can make it right, I promise.

46:26.380 --> 46:27.703
You'll have to trust me.

46:28.860 --> 46:30.770
- I trust you, Bearian.

46:30.770 --> 46:33.300
We stick together no matter what.

46:33.300 --> 46:37.740
- That's right, we're all
we have no matter what.

46:37.740 --> 46:38.743
- No matter what.

46:40.412 --> 46:42.410
- I need you to leave now, Randy.

46:42.410 --> 46:44.973
It won't be safe for you
here while I'm working.

46:46.460 --> 46:49.863
- Okay, I'll be right
outside if you need me.

47:44.641 --> 47:47.940
- Don't worry, Randy, it's not on.

47:47.940 --> 47:50.470
- What is this thing, Bearian?

47:50.470 --> 47:55.470
- It is my own invention I
created on my home world Bearia.

47:55.893 --> 47:57.850
It brought peace to my people,

47:57.850 --> 48:00.530
and now will bring peace to yours.

48:00.530 --> 48:03.060
It's called the Love Bomb.

48:03.060 --> 48:05.066
- How does it work?

48:05.066 --> 48:06.483
- It is a nuclear device,

48:07.360 --> 48:10.550
but I determined how to
restrain the destructive energy

48:10.550 --> 48:12.000
released by detonation,

48:12.000 --> 48:15.680
and to filter it in a way
that produces a radiation

48:15.680 --> 48:17.603
charged by love.

48:17.603 --> 48:18.520
Once detonated,

48:18.520 --> 48:21.580
the love radiation will
spread across the Earth,

48:21.580 --> 48:24.980
and all humans and animals
will live in peace.

48:24.980 --> 48:28.417
Things will be set right
again in your world.

48:28.417 --> 48:30.990
Then the great blackness in the universe

48:30.990 --> 48:34.053
will shrink to nothing,
and we will all be saved.

48:35.070 --> 48:38.867
- Okay Bearian, how do
we get it to Wyoming?

48:38.867 --> 48:41.517
- I won't be able to teleport both of us

48:41.517 --> 48:44.453
and the bomb without causing
great damage to myself.

48:45.590 --> 48:48.550
We're going to need a
helicopter, or something.

48:48.550 --> 48:49.650
There isn't much time.

48:50.890 --> 48:52.673
- A whirly bird?

48:52.673 --> 48:54.548
- A whirly bird.

49:07.868 --> 49:09.500
- Gitsburg, get in here.

49:09.500 --> 49:11.933
What are you waiting for, an invitation?

49:18.230 --> 49:20.070
You really screwed up this time, Ricky.

49:20.070 --> 49:21.030
Look at you.

49:21.030 --> 49:22.063
You're a mess.

49:23.430 --> 49:24.820
- Kiss my grits, Spears.

49:24.820 --> 49:26.510
Where were you when I needed you?

49:26.510 --> 49:29.813
You guys sat around and let
that imbecile cut off my hand.

49:31.190 --> 49:33.360
I'm done with you and
your band of gorillas.

49:33.360 --> 49:34.909
I want out.

49:34.909 --> 49:37.204
- Well, you're useless to us now, anyway.

49:37.204 --> 49:42.204
Unfortunately, it's
not gonna be that easy.

49:42.598 --> 49:44.684
- What do you think you're doing?

49:44.684 --> 49:47.801
We had a deal, Spears.

49:47.801 --> 49:52.051
- That's right, Ricky, we had
a deal, but you screwed it up.

49:52.051 --> 49:54.486
You didn't really think
we would let you walk out

49:54.486 --> 49:57.626
with everything that you know, did you?

49:57.626 --> 49:59.696
We're gonna put you on ice for a while,

49:59.696 --> 50:01.806
until I decide what to do with you.

50:01.806 --> 50:03.669
Take him out of here.

50:07.472 --> 50:09.868
- This ain't gonna work
out well for you, Spears.

50:09.868 --> 50:12.312
I'm not gonna forget this.

51:20.394 --> 51:22.648
I'm done with you and
your band of gorillas.

51:22.648 --> 51:24.066
